contract.name: Your First Contract
contract.description: We heard you are open to contract work! Help fill this order from the local pharmacy!

contract.name: Snack Attack
contract.description: For an unknown reason baked goods are flying off the shelves and more eggs are needed to restock!

contract.name: Egg Pre Orders
contract.description: Easter is around the corner, so naturally store are starting to stock up!

contract.name: Chocolate Refill
contract.description: The shelves of chocolate are empty at grocery stores, help fill the new orders!

contract.name: Arts and Crafts
contract.description: Kids are completing more arts and crafts projects than ever, we need more supplies!

contract.name: Shop at Home
contract.description: With the incredible surge of at home delivery for just about everything Quantum storage solutions are booming!

contract.name: Megg The 4th Be With You
contract.description: Levitation products and tricks are being cleared out of stores, suppliers need to refill orders!

contract.name: LEGACY: Laurel vs Yanny
contract.description: A Quantum rift is causing people to hear different words in a viral video. Scientists have a fix but they need your help.

contract.name: Supermarket Refill
contract.description: With so many restaurants closed, supermarkets weren't ready for Edible Egg demand for Mother's day omelettes!

contract.name: LEGACY: Home Renovations
contract.description: You've decided to build a new house! Why not make it yourself? You'll need a lot of eggs so get started!

contract.name: Personal Mobility
contract.description: The UnoWheel EggR personal mobility device was just released. Powered by Fusion Eggs, it has over 100 miles of range! Eggs are needed!

contract.name: LEGACY: All or Nothing
contract.description: A mysterious investor is looking for a lot of edible eggs. But he wants the full amount or nothing.

contract.name: Tachy-gone
contract.description: "Time tourism" broke all records this memorial day depleting tachyon egg inventories, time to help stock back up!

contract.name: LEGACY: SpaceEggs
contract.description: Spaceflight is booming due to re-usable rockets. Help fill the demand with this contract.

contract.name: Chocolate Rush
contract.description: For an unknown reason chocolate won't stay on the shelves, help meet the high demand!

contract.name: LEGACY: Anxiety Attack
contract.description: A new school year and political turmoil have everyone stressed out! A regimen of medical eggs are needed.

contract.name: Shipping Surge
contract.description: A surge in bulk shipping has created an opportunity for quantum egg farmers, join in on the rush!

contract.name: LEGACY: New Civilization
contract.description: A group of explorers are setting out to find new worlds, new civilizations. They are in need of fuel!

contract.name: Summer Solstice
contract.description: With summer solstice around the corner, the Global Egg Festival is about to kick off. Edible eggs are needed!

contract.name: LEGACY: Tool Time!
contract.description: It's father's day around the galaxy and power tools are flying off the shelves. Help restock!

contract.name: New Formula
contract.description: The genetic formula has been tweaked this year leading to record demand for firework eggs this year!

contract.name: LEGACY: Ouch!
contract.description: With all those new power tools out there, there are lots of minor injuries. First Aid!

contract.name: Heating Up
contract.description: Summer is heating up and you know what that means.... Waterballoon fight!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Last Minute
contract.description: More fireworks are needed ASAP!

contract.name: Hot Fireworks
contract.description: With a surge in at-home fireworks shows, burn treatments are flying off the shelves, help restock!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Time Tourism
contract.description: (From Memorial Day 2018) so called "Time Tourism" is booming and Tachyon eggs are in short supply!

contract.name: E-Day
contract.description: Egg Day is once again upon us (July 14), and everyone is looking for the classic.

contract.name: LEGGACY: Egg Day 2018
contract.description: Some folks like to celebrate Egg Day with a bang!

contract.name: Summer Fitness
contract.description: August is the most popular month to vacation, people are dieting to get their bodies ready for the beach!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Engage!
contract.description: (2018) The Federation of planets needs more fuel for their star fleet!

contract.name: Secret Projects
contract.description: Space Agencies around the globe are expanding deep space exploration, Rocket Fuel is in short supply!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Summer Sunset
contract.description: The local town has commissioned you to create the waterballoons for the end of summer waterballoon fight! (2018)

contract.name: Video Games
contract.description: With folks playing more PC and Console games than ever before, home energy needs are up!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Just Chocolate
contract.description: Sometimes chocolate demand spikes, and all we gotta do as egg farmers is make more chocolate. (2018)

contract.name: Ion Drive
contract.description: Aerospace companies need Fusion eggs for an experimental Ion Thruster project.

contract.name: LEGGACY: Nostalgia
contract.description: July 14 (2018) is Egg Day around the galaxy and everyone like to celebrate with the egg that started it all...

contract.name: Cool Off
contract.description: As heat waves take over the country, waterballoons are in short supply!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Getting Ready
contract.description: With 4th of July (2018) nearing in the States, scientists have found a new way to meet the demand for fireworks...

contract.name: Orbital Fueling
contract.description: A new orbital fueling rig has begun operation, it needs copious amounts of Quantum Eggs!

contract.name: LEGGACY: A Clever Solution
contract.description: As drought wreaks havoc on agriculture, farmers are looking for water in unusual places... (2018)

contract.name: Bluetooth Pigs
contract.description: Bluetooth enabled pigs are the new hot pet! Neuro-implant makers need more materials!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Mother's Day Brunch
contract.description: Mothers all over the galaxy are requesting omelettes and french toast for breakfast! (2018)

contract.name: Space Food
contract.description: A biomedical firm is developing food for space travelers based heavily on superfood eggs.

contract.name: LEGGACY: Complex Costumes
contract.description: Halloween (2018) costume manufacturing has started. These are sophisticated scary costumes that need some high tech components.

contract.name: Made In Space
contract.description: A space exploration firm is building a spaceship factory.. in space!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Chocolate!
contract.description: Didn't take scientists long to figure out the smart thing to do was to just make chickens lay chocolate eggs. (2018)

contract.name: Hydrogen Dreams
contract.description: After a hydrogen fuel cell car company was revealed to be a fraud, Teslegg Fusion car sales are surging!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Super Food Drive
contract.description: (2018) Egg Farmers have flocked to high value eggs leaving people hungry! We need some Superfood eggs stat!

contract.name: Color Change
contract.description: As the leaves change color so do the eggs. Help meet seasonal demand!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Fall Festival Competition
contract.description: The (2018) Fall Festival egg laying competition is here!

contract.name: Fall Flu
contract.description: Flu season is getting started, and folks are stocking up preventative medications!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Pumpkin Crunch
contract.description: (2018) Pumpkins are in super high demand... leave it to the chickens to deliver the goods!

contract.name: Tricker Treats
contract.description: Time to help make everyone's favorite Halloween treat!

contract.name: LEGGACY: A New Sun
contract.description: (2018) A new solar system has been found with multiple habitable planets in need of terraforming!

contract.name: Quantum Ballot Box
contract.description: The new Quantum Ballot boxes can securely store millions of ballots. Make sure you (or your parents) are planning to vote!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Moon Food
contract.description: (2019) Moon colony food stores were tainted without government food inspectors to check for contaminants. Help send some food!

contract.name: Last Minute Decoration
contract.description: Family meetings were called, one common conclusion: We need more pumpkins!

contract.name: LEGGACY: Halloween Blitz
contract.description: (2018) Pumpkin demand is overwhelming! A quick contract for big money!
